    "instruction": "Set up the Airbyte Cloud connection for the already configured Sample Data (Faker) source and enable daily full-refresh-overwrite syncs for the users, products, and purchases streams into the Supabase/PostgreSQL warehouse.",
    "task_type": "CONNECTION_SETUP",
    "tool": "AirbyteConnector",
    "tool_args": {
      "source_name": "Sample Data (Faker)",
      "streams": ["users", "products", "purchases"],
